cast.overview: The true story of Marine Corporal Megan Leavey, who forms a powerful bond with an aggressive combat dog, Rex. While deployed in Iraq, the two complete more than 100 missions and save countless lives, until an IED explosion puts their faithfulness to the test.
cast.title: Megan Leavey

details.biography:
Tyler Buckingham is an actor, stuntman, writer, director, and producer from Big Rapids, Michigan.

He can be seen on the television shows: The Walking Dead (2009), The Vampire Diaries (2009), Doom Patrol (2019), and Halt and Catch Fire (2014); and in the feature films: Meagan Leavey (2017), The Canadoo (2016), and Pageant Material (2019).
details.name: Tyler Buckingham
